description:
Premium Office Space

Modern 2,500 sq ft office on the 4th floor with panoramic city views. Features include high-speed internet, 24/7 security, and ample parking. Perfect for IT companies and tech startups.

Amenities: Wi-Fi, AC, Power Backup, Cafeteria

  • 2,500 square feet
  • 4th Floor Location
  • 24/7 Security & Parking
  • High-speed Internet Ready

Medical Office Suite

Well-designed 2,000 sq ft medical office with reception area, consultation rooms, and storage. Ideal for clinics and healthcare services with excellent patient accessibility.

Features: Waiting Area, Private Rooms, Storage

  • 2,000 square feet
  • Multiple Consultation Rooms
  • Reception & Waiting Area
  • Ground Floor Access

Premium Penthouse Office

Spacious 3,000 sq ft top-floor premium office with stunning skyline views. Features executive cabins, conference room, and modern interiors. Prime location for corporate headquarters.

Premium Features: Top Floor, Skyline View, Executive Layout

  • 3,000 square feet
  • Top Floor (5th)
  • Executive Cabins
  • Conference Room
  • Panoramic City Views

Ground Floor Residential Unit

Cozy 1,200 sq ft ground floor apartment with garden access. Features 2 bedrooms, modern kitchen, and peaceful ambiance. Perfect for small families seeking comfort.

Amenities: Garden, Parking, Security, Maintenance

  • 1,200 square feet
  • 2 Bedrooms
  • Garden Access
  • Ground Floor Convenience

Bright 2nd Floor Apartment

Airy 1,400 sq ft second floor unit with natural lighting and balcony. Modern amenities, 2 bedrooms, spacious living area. Great for families looking for a peaceful residential space.

Features: Balcony, Natural Light, Elevator Access

  • 1,400 square feet
  • 2 Bedrooms
  • Balcony with Views
  • Elevator Access

Spacious 3rd Floor Unit

Premium 1,600 sq ft residential unit on 3rd floor with excellent ventilation. 3 bedrooms, modular kitchen, and premium fixtures. Ideal for growing families seeking extra space.

Premium Features: 3 Bedrooms, Modular Kitchen, Premium Finish

  • 1,600 square feet
  • 3 Bedrooms
  • Modular Kitchen
  • Premium Fixtures

Top Floor Residential

Elegant 1,400 sq ft top floor apartment with terrace access. Features 2 bedrooms, contemporary design, and panoramic views. Perfect for professionals seeking a modern lifestyle.

Special Features: Terrace Access, Top Floor, City Views

  • 1,400 square feet
  • 2 Bedrooms
  • Terrace Access
  • Panoramic Views

Prime Ground Floor Retail

High-visibility 800 sq ft retail space with street frontage. Perfect for food retail, convenience stores, or cafes. Heavy foot traffic area with excellent business potential.

Business Advantages: Street Access, High Footfall, Display Windows

  • 800 square feet
  • Ground Floor
  • Street Frontage
  • High Visibility

Compact Retail Space

Cozy 600 sq ft ground floor retail unit ideal for boutiques, salons, or service businesses. Corner location with good visibility and convenient customer access.

Features: Corner Unit, Ground Access, Compact Layout

  • 600 square feet
  • Corner Location
  • Ground Floor
  • High Visibility

Mixed Use Office Space

Versatile 1,800 sq ft second floor space suitable for office or showroom use. Open layout with flexible configuration options. Ideal for businesses needing display and work areas.

Flexible Options: Open Layout, Multi-Purpose, Good Lighting

  • Open Floor Plan
